T02TD3377E:52b-1: aushn'i sha bi dza y'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3377E:52b-3: gtsug tor rnam par rgyal ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3377E:52b-4: gtsug tor rnam par rgyal ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3377E:52b-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho gas zla ba la bhr'um dkar po yongs su gyur pa las zhal gsum spyan gsum ma /
T02TD3377E:52b-6: lang tsho gsar la bab pa /
T02TD3377E:52b-7: lha rdzas kyi rgyan dang na bza' dang ldan pa /
T02TD3377E:52b-8: phyag brgyad pa'i gtsug tor rnam par rgyal ma bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3377E:52b-9: ser po dang nag po ni g-yas pa dang cig shos kyi zhal lo //
T02TD3377E:52b-10: g-yas kyi phyag bzhi rnams su sna tshogs kyi rdo rje dang /
T02TD3377E:52b-11: padma la gnas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sku dang /
T02TD3377E:52b-14: g-yon gyi phyag bzhi rnams su gzhu dang /
T02TD3377E:52b-15: sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhabs pa dang /
T02TD3377E:52b-18: mchod rten gyi phug gi khong na gnas par bskyed la /
T02TD3377E:52b-19: padma la gnas pa'i sa bon snying gar bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3377E:52b-20: de'i rjes su spyi bo dang /
T02TD3377E:52b-24: rkang pa rnams su go rims bzhin du h'um tr'am hr'i:aam aa:zhes bya ba'i yi ge'i rnam par bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3377E:52b-27: gtsug tor rnam par rgyal ma'i sgrub pa'i thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3377E:52b-28: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3377E:52b-29: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur cing zhus so//
